get/0000018e-281e-d1b8-a5de-e9de10d30000</guid></item><item><title>在所有会议之母上，以色列妇女希望在开创性反战运动的成功基础上再接再厉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</link><description>上周在耶路撒冷举行的一次会议探讨了母性的概念及其在政治组织和激进主义中的作用，团结是当前各种运动（从母亲支持生命到母亲反对暴力）之间的关键目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 11:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</guid></item><item><title>斋月祈祷将于周一在耶路撒冷开始，使加沙战争的紧张局势达到潜在的临界点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</link><description>在政府决定在哈马斯战争期间不再实施新的入境限制后，数千名穆斯林信徒抵达阿克萨/圣殿山大院将使以色列的政策面临考验。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席塞法迪拉比：如果他们强迫我们参军，我们都会离开这个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</link><description>首席拉比发表上述言论之际，该州向高等法院解释为什么不征召极端正统派男子入伍——尽管豁免他们服役的法律已经到期</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家在耶路撒冷附近发现迦南“旭日神庙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-10/ty-article/archae